## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **FLASH-RT 2014 Favaudon Sci Trans Med preclinical → 2018 first patient (Bourhis Lausanne) → 2022 UPenn first proton FLASH** = 1초 미만 ultra-high dose-rate paradigm shift. 정상조직 보존 + 종양 효능 dissociation — 분자 산소 고갈 + ROS DNA 결합 hypothesis. quantum-VQE 의 분자 산소 + ROS + DNA 결합 paradigm fit.
2. **proton therapy Loma Linda 1990 + MGH 2001 + Mayo 2014** = Bragg peak — 정상조직 후방 dose 0. IMPT spot-scanning + passive scattering 두 delivery. 한국 삼성서울병원 + 국립암센터 + KIRAMS 양성자 commercial.
3. **carbon ion 1994 GSI Germany → 2003 NIRS Japan first commercial → 2024 14+ centers (Italy + Japan + Germany + Austria + China)** = high LET — radioresistant tumor (sarcoma + GBM + 췌장암). 한국 carbon ion 시설 부재 — KIRAMS R&D 진행.
4. **MR-Linac Elekta Unity 2018 + ViewRay MRIdian** = adaptive RT — real-time MR-guided per-fraction re-planning. 2024 commercial 확산.
5. **BgRT RefleXion 2023** = biology-guided RT — PET-guided real-time tumor tracking. FDG + PSMA tracer real-time 추적 + dose delivery — first regulatory clearance.
6. **PEMBRO-RT 2019 + abscopal effect** = 방사선 + PD-1 immune 시너지. RT 가 immune cold-to-hot transformation + abscopal off-target tumor regression. 임상 Phase 2/3 다수 진행.
7. **amifostine Ethyol 1995 + palifermin Kepivance 2004** = radioprotector + 점막 보호 paradigm. 침샘 + 점막 + 식도염 toxicity 완화. quantum-VQE 의 radioprotector pocket + KGF 결합 modeling.
8. **방사선 secondary cancer pediatric long-term concern** = pediatric RT 후 secondary malig 위험 — proton 의 Bragg peak 가 정상조직 dose 감소 → secondary cancer 위험 감소 paradigm. cross-pediatric_rare.
9. **Monte Carlo TOPAS + GEANT4 simulation** = 방사선 분포 + dose 분포 + microdosimetry 정밀 simulation. 양자 시뮬레이션 + 분자 수준 RT 결합 paradigm.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, precision RT modality 임상 의미 한정.

